data.description: Under Construction. The Cali is a spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath open concept home on an oversized home site in Bentwood. This open floor plan is great for both families and entertaining and offers a large kitchen with flow through counter top island, Amana Stainless Steal appliances and ample corner pantry. The covered Lanai opens up to the large back yard where you can relax and enjoy the peace & quite overlooking Conservation of trees. Lake Denham is an absolutely beautiful neighborhood that puts you in the middle of the best that Lake County has to offer. The neighborhood is located within Leesburg City Limits in Lake County. It is just a few minutes to shopping, movie theaters, restaurants, Griffin State Park, boat ramps to Beautiful Lake Harris and only 5 minutes to Downtown Leesburg. *Photos are of similar model but not that of exact house. Please note that no representations or warranties are made regarding school districts or school assignments; you should conduct your own investigation regarding current and future schools and school boundaries.*
